@6879=~Elixir of Renewed Spirit~
@6880=~This is one of the most powerful potions a wizard can create. Upon drinking it, one is instantly revitalized, as one would from a full night's sleep. Such an effect would allow a wizard or another spellcaster to cast all of their spells again. While it may seem that, if one was a powerful enough wizard, one could create one of these potions with pure magic, drink it to regain the spells, and repeat the process ad infinitum, there is no known way to create one of these potions without consuming large amounts of rare components. In trying to create many of these potions, one quickly runs out of components. In addition, each of these potions takes over a week to craft, even by a master wizard. Since they are so difficult to make, mages who own them are not quick to use them. As a result, there are still a few of these potions lying around throughout the Realms, waiting to be used.

