@16596=~This extremely powerful wand was created by Ulcaster himself, back when he and his school were alive and well. It may very well be an artifact, for it is the only known wand of its kind. Perhaps the wand is too difficult for anyone other than an archmage to create, but one could only know for sure if one knew how to create it. Alas, Ulcaster never wrote down the secret of the wand's construction. Maybe one could pry the secret out of his ghost, but probably not.

